{"tid":2363815,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"「我爸爸是香港警察」","createTime":"2021-01-12T13:17:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T13:23:02.000Z","uid":20820,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5cc5b491fbda14e74639e2394ae746f24b4a7382","tid":2363815,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T13:17:41.000Z","msg":"2021年1月10日是我国首个人民警察节。在2019年，冲在止暴制乱最前线的香港警察一定给大家留下了深刻印象。仅3万人守护700万人的城市，他们身历险境，忍辱负重，自己与家庭遭到黑暴起底，孩子在学校里或受到不公平对待，甚至遭受霸凌&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n一位9岁的香港小朋友，因为爸爸是香港警察，在整整一年的时间里，自己被「黄师」屡屡打击嘲讽，小朋友的家庭也遭到曝光起底。2020年6月30日香港国安法实施后，香港由乱向治，小朋友的家庭也经历「破晓」重见曙光。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4yOemjOpt9Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4yOemjOpt9Y&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJubis81FSeaDeH2Oz4vdBzj8%3D&h=eefaee00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4yOemjOpt9Y</a><br />\n<br />\n喊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好彩有国安法"},{"pid":"f57db480ce286e12d9414dfd140f126a733b6733","tid":2363815,"uid":85586,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T13:20:56.000Z","msg":"爸爸殺人就得<br />\n個仔俾人蝦就唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed9d72cfd8a688db5cb600885eacfc98eba96f6","tid":2363815,"uid":55905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T13:21:22.000Z","msg":"你老母比狗屌呀？寫中文得唔撚得呀？邊撚個識睇呢d鬼畫符呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b9e4770bdc113b28920164286edbeeadbb4de3","tid":2363815,"uid":20820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ed9d72cfd8a688db5cb600885eacfc98eba96f6","tid":2363815,"uid":55905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T13:21:22.000Z","msg":"你老母比狗屌呀？寫中文得唔撚得呀？邊撚個識睇呢d鬼畫符呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.